snippet.title: TT Isle of Man - Ride on the Edge 3 | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
𝐓𝐇𝐈𝐒 is the moment you've been waiting for.
𝐓𝐇𝐈𝐒 is your moment.
𝐓𝐇𝐈𝐒 is the 𝐈𝐬𝐥𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐌𝐚𝐧 𝐓𝐓.

• Ride on 32 different circuits, including current and historical races.
• Nearly 40 Superbike and Supersport motorbikes and riders.
• Unleash your machine with upgraded physics and motorbike customization.
• A new "Open Roads" feature, allowing you to travel freely on 200km of roads and find points of interest and challenges to complete.

Coming in May 2023 on PC and Consoles.
